item.title: By: Conor O'Neill
item.dc:creator: Conor O'Neill
item.description:
It would be a great opportunity and the timing is nearly perfect for our launch.
However I imagine the overall cost will be several thousand including flights/attendance etc and we couldn't risk it being a flop.
Is EI offering any assistance to companies attending?
